body:
hi this is my first post!
This is how to become a pvp god like NekoWOlf (MEEE!!!)
Step 1:
Dont stop moving in a pvp battle, make sure to move around fast! This term is called "strafing"

Step 2:
Click as fast as you possibly can!!! This term is called "jitterclicking"

Step 3:
Make sure to always have your mouse on your target!

Step 4:
Have lots of fun!

Hope you guys get good and enjoy!
nekowolf out!
